item.title: About
item.description: HI, I am Han Wu, majoring in Communication Engineering. I have broad interests within Communication Engineering fields from wireless communication, information theory to signal processing. For more information, please visit my personal webpage (It’s still been made). This is my personal blog, where I will share my experience and knowledge. If you have any question about a blog, please go to the github issue to ask questions. In order to keep the webpage tidy and avoid nonsense comments, I am not going to use comment system. If you think I am infringing your copyright, please contact me through github issue, and I will remove the content.
